107
04:36:36,000 --> 04:36:42,000
This shows where your money is going.
API versus agent versus ingestion versus pgvector versus redis.

108
04:36:42,000 --> 04:36:48,000
Panel two. Cost per Query in cents.
Stat panel using financial_rag:cost_per_query_cents:1h.

109
04:36:48,000 --> 04:36:54,000
This shows your unit economics.
How much each query costs to run.

110
04:36:54,000 --> 04:37:00,000
