Gauge panel using financial_rag:slo_availability:error_budget_remaining.

111
04:37:00,000 --> 04:37:06,000
Color thresholds. Red at 0 percent, yellow at 25 percent, green at 50 percent.

112
04:37:06,000 --> 04:37:12,000
Panel four. LLM Token Cost per hour.
Time series panel using rate of financial_rag_llm_cost_usd_total.

113
04:37:12,000 --> 04:37:18,000
Apply the budget alerts.
Create a PrometheusRule for FinOps.

114
04:37:18,000 --> 04:37:24,000
MonthlyBudgetExceeded alert.
Triggers if sum of kubecost_cluster_costs_total in financial-rag namespace exceeds 5000.

115
04:37:24,000 --> 04:37:30,000
For 1 hour. Severity warning, team finops.

116
04:37:30,000 --> 04:37:36,000
LLMCostSpike alert.
Triggers if rate of LLM cost per hour exceeds 50 dollars.

117
04:37:36,000 --> 04:37:42,000
For 15 minutes. Severity warning, team finops.

118
04:37:42,000 --> 04:37:48,000
Apply the budget alerts.
kubectl apply with the PrometheusRule YAML.

119
04:37:48,000 --> 04:37:54,000
Import the dashboard via Grafana UI.
Dashboards, Import, upload the JSON file.

120
04:37:54,000 --> 04:38:00,000
Our FinOps dashboard is complete.
Cost and efficiency metrics are now visible.


