[## [SECTION: Common Errors and Fixes — Phases 11 & 12]]


135
04:39:24,000 --> 04:39:30,000
Let me walk through common errors in Phases 11 and 12.
And how to fix them.

136
04:39:30,000 --> 04:39:36,000
Error one. OTLPSpanExporter failed to export.
The OpenTelemetry Collector is not running.

137
04:39:36,000 --> 04:39:42,000
Check kubectl get pods in the financial-rag namespace for opentelemetry-collector.
If not running, check the logs and restart.

138
04:39:42,000 --> 04:39:48,000
Error two. Traces not in Jaeger.
Sampling rate is too low.

139
04:39:48,000 --> 04:39:54,000
Set OTEL_TRACE_SAMPLE_RATE to 1.0 temporarily in development.
This captures 100 percent of traces for debugging.

140
04:39:54,000 --> 04:40:00,000
Error three. engine.sync_engine AttributeError.
SQLAlchemy async engine issue.

141
04:40:00,000 --> 04:40:06,000
Call configure_tracing after get_db_client connects.
The engine must be initialised before instrumentation.

142
04:40:06,000 --> 04:40:12,000
Error four. SLO recording rules not found.
Prometheus is not loading the rules.

143
04:40:12,000 --> 04:40:18,000
Check the label release equals kube-prometheus-stack on the PrometheusRule.
The Prometheus operator requires this label.

144
04:40:18,000 --> 04:40:24,000
Error five. Conftest deny on compliant pod.
Missing required label.

145
04:40:24,000 --> 04:40:30,000
Add app.kubernetes.io/component label to the pod spec.
The Rego policy requires this label for Cilium selectors.

146
04:40:30,000 --> 04:40:36,000
Error six. VPA shows no recommendations.
Insufficient history.

147
04:40:36,000 --> 04:40:42,000
Wait 24 to 48 hours after applying VPA.
The recommender needs time to collect usage data.

148
04:40:42,000 --> 04:40:48,000
Error seven. Velero backup PartiallyFailed.
PVC snapshot permissions missing.

149
04:40:48,000 --> 04:40:54,000
Verify velero-credentials has ec2:CreateSnapshot IAM permission.
The role must allow snapshot creation.

150
04:40:54,000 --> 04:41:00,000
Error eight. Production readiness check fails.
Pods using latest image tag.

151
04:41:00,000 --> 04:41:06,000
Pin image tags in values.prod.yaml to a semver or SHA.
Never use latest in production.

152
04:41:06,000 --> 04:41:12,000
Error nine. Grafana no data on FinOps panels.
Kubecost is not scraping.

153
04:41:12,000 --> 04:41:18,000
Check Kubecost ServiceMonitor and the release label.
Prometheus must be configured to scrape Kubecost.

154
04:41:18,000 --> 04:41:24,000
Error ten. conftest verify test failures.
Policy logic error.

155
04:41:24,000 --> 04:41:30,000
Run opa test policies/rego/ dash v directly.
This shows which specific tests are failing.

156
04:41:30,000 --> 04:41:36,000
Bookmark this section.
When you hit an error, you'll know exactly where to look.

157
